OL,3,CGuidelines for public bodies 'expected
OL,4,Cby summer' after 'woman' ruling
OL,6,FBritain's equalities watchdog said
OL,7,FWednesday's gender ruling means trans
OL,8,Fwomen can not use single-sex changing
OL,9,Frooms, toilets or compete in women's
OL,10,Fsports, as ITV News' Rachel Younger
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FThe equalities watchdog is looking to
OL,14,Fupdate its guidance for service
OL,15,Fproviders and public bodies by "this
OL,16,Fsummer" after the Supreme Court ruled
OL,17,Fthat a woman is defined in law by
OL,18,F"biological sex".
