OL,6,FThe ruling on Wednesday said that the
OL,7,Fterms "woman" and "sex" in the 2010
OL,8,FEquality Act "refer to a biological
OL,9,Fwoman and biological sex", meaning
OL,10,Ftransgender women with a gender
OL,11,Frecognition certificate (GRC) can be
OL,12,Fexcluded from single-sex spaces if
OL,13,F"proportionate", the Supreme Court
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FIn light of the ruling, organisations
OL,17,Fhave already begun reviewing policy,
OL,18,Fwith British Transport Police (BTP)
OL,19,Fannouncing on Thursday it will adopt
OL,20,Fan "interim position" on its strip
OL,21,Fsearch policy.
