OL,6,FIt said trans people held in custody
OL,7,Fstrip searched by an officer in line
OL,8,Fwith their birth sex - meaning trans
OL,9,Fwomen in custody will be searched by
OL,10,Fmale officers, while officers who are
OL,11,Ftrans women will no longer be able to
OL,12,Fsearch female detainees.
OL,14,FThe public confirmation of a policy
OL,15,Fchange came as Equality and Human
OL,16,FRights Commission (EHRC) chairwoman
OL,17,FBaroness Kishwer Falkner said the
OL,18,Fruling provided clarity to
OL,19,Forganisations and they should be
OL,20,F"taking care" to look at the "very
OL,21,Freadable judgment".
