OL,6,F"Single-sex services like changing
OL,7,Frooms must be based on biological
OL,8,Fsex," she told BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,9,FProgramme.
OL,11,F"If a male person is allowed to use a
OL,12,Fwomen-only service or facility, it
OL,13,Fisn't any longer single-sex, then it
OL,14,Fbecomes a mixed-sex space.
