OL,6,F"But I have to say, there's no law
OL,7,Fthat forces organisations, service
OL,8,Fproviders, to provide a single-sex
OL,9,Fspace, and there is no law against
OL,10,Fthem providing a third space, an
OL,11,Fadditional space, such as unisex
OL,12,Ftoilets for example, or changing
OL,13,Frooms."
OL,15,FShe suggested trans rights
OL,16,Forganisations "should be using their
OL,17,Fpowers of advocacy to ask for those
OL,18,Fthird spaces".
