OL,6,FThe decision by the Supreme Court was
OL,7,Fhailed by women's rights campaigners,
OL,8,Fbut trans communities are "devastated"
OL,9,Fby the ruling.
OL,11,FHelen Belcher, the chair of
OL,12,FTransActual, said: "The Supreme Court
OL,13,Fchose not to hear from any trans
OL,14,Fpeople, preferring instead to listen
OL,15,Fto exclusionary groups.
