OL,3,CGuidelines for public bodies 'expected
OL,4,Cby summer' after 'woman' ruling
OL,6,F"As a result, instead of bringing
OL,7,Fclarity, the Supreme Court has made a
OL,8,Fruling which appears to contain a
OL,9,Fnumber of contradictions. Irrespective
OL,10,Fof the small print, the intent seems
OL,11,Fclear: to exclude trans people
OL,12,Fwholesale from participating in UK
OL,13,Fsociety. Today, we are feeling very
OL,14,Fexcluded."
OL,16,FBaroness Falkner said while the ruling
OL,17,Fis a "victory for common sense", this
OL,18,Fis only the case "if you recognise
OL,19,Fthat trans people exist".
