OL,6,FRegarding single-sex hospital wards,
OL,7,FBaroness Falkner said the NHS will
OL,8,F"have to change" its 2019 policy,
OL,9,Fwhich says that trans people "should
OL,10,Fbe accommodated according to their
OL,11,Fpresentation".
OL,13,FOfficials said they were already
OL,14,Fupdating the guidance, but the
OL,15,Fjudgment will be considered as they
OL,16,Fmove forward.
OL,18,FAs Britain's independent equality
OL,19,Fregulator, the EHRC assisted the court
OL,20,Fin assessing the legal and practical
OL,21,Fimplications of Wednesday's case.
