OL,6,FTheir revised code of practice, which
OL,7,Fis subject to ministerial approval, is
OL,8,Fexpected to be laid before Parliament
OL,9,F"before the summer recess".
OL,11,F"We will be working at pace to
OL,12,Fincorporate the implications of this
OL,13,Fjudgment into the updated Code, which
OL,14,Fsupports service providers, public
OL,15,Fbodies and associations to understand
OL,16,Ftheir duties under the Equality Act
OL,17,Fand put them into practice," it said
OL,18,Fin a statement.
