OL,6,FBaroness Falkner said the commission
OL,7,Fevaluates when the law is not followed
OL,8,Fby organisations and can speak to
OL,9,Fthose bodies, or "use enforcement,
OL,10,Fcompliance tools or whatever, we will
OL,11,Fbe continuing to do that".
OL,13,FSecondary Care Secretary, Karin Smyth,
OL,14,Fsaid providers have a responsibility
OL,15,Fto ensure they comply with the law.
OL,17,FShe told reporters: "The Equality Act
OL,18,Fis the same today as it was yesterday.
OL,19,FThis government has always been
OL,20,Fcommitted to single sex places for
OL,21,Fwomen.
